<Body>
	<Title>城东区发生疑似食物中毒事件 全力救治中毒患者</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2014年03月11日08:10</ReportTime> 来源：青海新闻网  作者：徐顺凯

<Content>
		<Paragraph>
			<Sentence>
				<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e1"><Participant sid="s">青海新闻网</Participant><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">讯</Denoter></Event>
				<Event eid="e2"><Time tid="t2" type="relTime">3月10日凌晨</Time>，<Participant sid="s2">西宁市委、市政府</Participant><Denoter did="d2" type="action">接报</Denoter></Event>
				<Event eid="e3"><Location lid="l3">城东区</Location>发生一起因市民婚宴引起的<Denoter did="d3" type="emergency">疑似食物中毒</Denoter>事件</Event>后，
<Event eid="e4">市主要<Participant sid="s4,s5,s6">领导</Participant>高度<Denoter did="d4" type="action">重视</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e5">立即作出<Denoter did="d5" type="action">批示</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e6"><Denoter did="d6" type="action">要求</Denoter><Participant oid="o6">医院和相关部门</Participant>全力以赴<Object oid="o6">做好患者救治工作</Object></Event>。</Sentence>
<Sentence><Event eid="e7"><Time tid="t7" type="relTime">上午</Time>一<Denoter did="d7" type="action">上班</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e8"><Participant sid="s8,s7,s9,s10,s11">省委常委、市委书记毛小兵，副市长、市公安局局长张谦，副市长王彤及城东区委区政府、市食品药品监督等部门负责人</Participant><Denoter did="d8" type="movement">赶赴</Denoter><Location lid="l8" type="destination">省人民医院和省儿童医院</Location></Event>，<Event eid="e9"><Denoter did="d9" type="action">看望慰问</Denoter>事件中的<Participant oid="o9">24名患者</Participant></Event>，<Event eid="e10"><Denoter did="d10" type="action">安抚</Denoter><Participant oid="o10">病人家属</Participant></Event>，<Event eid="e11"><Denoter did="d11" type="action">表达</Denoter><Participant oid="o11">党和政府的高度关切</Participant></Event>。</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>
		<Paragraph>　　
<Sentence><Event eid="e12">在<Location lid="l12">省人民医院急诊中心治疗室</Location>，<Participant sid="s12">毛小兵</Participant>详细<Denoter did="d12" type="action">询问</Denoter><Participant oid="o12">医院治疗和病人康复情况</Participant></Event>。</Sentence>
<Sentence>当<Event eid="e13"><Denoter did="d13" type="perception">听到</Denoter><Participant oid="o13">所有病人生命体征稳定、无生命危险</Participant></Event>时，
<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e14"><Participant sid="s14,s13">毛小兵</Participant><Denoter did="d14" type="perception">感到</Denoter>十分欣慰</Event>，<Event eid="e15"><Participant sid="s15,s16,s17,s18,s20">他</Participant><Denoter did="d15" type="movement">来到</Denoter><Location lid="l15" type="destination">病床前</Location></Event>，<Event eid="e16">与<Participant oid="o16">患者</Participant>亲切<Denoter did="d16" type="action">交谈</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e17">仔细<Denoter did="d17" type="action">了解</Denoter><Object oid="o17">病情</Object></Event>，并<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e18"><Denoter did="d18" type="statement">表示</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e19"><Participant sid="s19">党和政府</Participant>一定会高度<Denoter did="d19" type="action">重视</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e20" type="thoughtevent"><Denoter did="d20" type="action">希望</Denoter><Participant oid="o20,s21,s22">患者</Participant>不要有心理压力</Event>，<Event eid="e21">积极<Denoter did="d21" type="action">配合</Denoter><Object oid="o21">治疗</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e22"><Denoter did="d22" type="action">争取</Denoter>早日康复</Event>。</Sentence>
<Sentence>在
<Event eid="e23"><Denoter did="d23" type="action">看望</Denoter>省儿童医院收治的<Participant oid="o23">3名儿童患者</Participant></Event>时，
<Event eid="e24" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s24,s26">毛小兵</Participant><Denoter did="d24" type="action">鼓励</Denoter><Participant oid="o24,s24">孩子们</Participant>不要害怕</Event>，
<Event eid="e25">好好<Denoter did="d25" type="action">配合</Denoter><Object oid="o25">治疗</Object></Event>，
<Event eid="e26" type="thoughtevent"><Denoter did="d26" type="action">要求</Denoter><Participant oid="o26,s27,s28">院方</Participant>
<Event eid="e27">精心<Denoter did="d" type="operation">治疗</Denoter></Event>、
<Event eid="e28">精心<Denoter did="d" type="operation">护理</Denoter></Event>，尽快使孩子们康复</Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph>　　
<Sentence><Event eid="e29">在<Location lid="l29">现场</Location>，<Participant sid="s29,s33">毛小兵</Participant><Denoter did="d29" type="action">听取</Denoter>了城东区政府和医院专家组的<Object oid="o29">情况汇报</Object>
				</Event>，
对<Event eid="e30"><Participant sid="s30,s31,s32">各相关部门</Participant>快速<Denoter did="d30" type="operation">启动</Denoter><Object oid="o30">应急预案</Object></Event>、
<Event eid="e31">积极<Denoter did="d31" type="operation">组织</Denoter><Object oid="o31">抢救</Object></Event>、
<Event eid="e32">迅速<Denoter did="d32" type="action">稳定</Denoter><Object oid="o32">病情</Object></Event>等
<Event eid="e33"><Object oid="o33">各项工作</Object><Denoter did="d33" type="action">给予</Denoter>了充分<Object oid="o33">肯定</Object></Event>，
<Event eid="e34">对医护人员的辛勤<Object oid="o34">救治工作</Object>表示<Denoter did="d34" type="action">感谢</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>
		<Paragraph>　　
<Sentence>
<Event eid="e35"><Time tid="t35" type="relTime">截至发稿前</Time>，<Participant  oid="o35">24名患者</Participant>生命体征稳定，经<Denoter did="d35" type="operation">治疗</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e36"><Participant sid="s36">10人</Participant>恢复正常<Denoter did="d36" type="action">回家</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e37"><Participant oid="o37">其余病患</Participant>仍留在<Location lid="l37">医院</Location><Denoter did="d37" type="perception">观察</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
	</Content>
